\"> later, in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram></gramGrp>, merely <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">to have connexion with</tr_> a woman, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cerc.\">Cerc.</a></author> </bibl> l.c., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg047:12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eun.\">Eun.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg033:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Merc.Cond.\">Merc.Cond.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope></bibl>, etc.:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, of the woman, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὐκ ὀπύουσιν ἀλλ᾽ ὀπύονται [γυναῖκες]</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> </bibl> </cit> l.c., cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">AP</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.56.7</biblScope> </bibl> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Pall.</author> </bibl>); <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔνθ᾽ ἂν εὕρῃ τὸν ἄρρενα ὑπὸ τῆς θηλείας ὀπυιόμενον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:19:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.2</biblScope></bibl></cit>. (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὀπύ(ς᾽ <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"i